# ScoopnSmiles 🍰

ScoopnSmiles is a full-stack bakery ordering platform that allows users to browse products, place orders, and track their purchases online.

## Tech Stack

Frontend
- Next.js / React
- TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS

Backend
- Node.js
- Express.js

ML Backend
- Python
- Data processing scripts

## Features

- User authentication (Sign In / Sign Up)
- Product browsing
- Cart and checkout
- Order tracking
- Admin dashboard
- Machine learning support for product analysis

